"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-ioc-to-pick-los-angeles-paris-for-2024-or-2028-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  LAUSANNE, July 12: Finally, Los Angeles and Paris have their Olympic hosting destiny in their own hands.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3328272467595065e-14, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they can agree who goes first, each city will be awarded either the 2024 or 2028 Summer Games in September.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"International Olympic Committee members voted unanimously on Tuesday to seek a consensus three-way deal between the two bid cities and the IOC executive board.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talks will open with Paris widely seen as the favorite for 2024.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If a deal falls through, only the 2024 hosting rights will be voted on when the IOC next meets, on Sept. 13 in Lima, Peru.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"score\": 0.9999999702063183, \"rank\": 2.9219019615161643e-08, \"text\": \"Lima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\"}, {\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"score\": 0.999907050624149, \"rank\": 9.2957161915601e-05, \"text\": \"Peru\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, an agreement seemed assured, judging by the reaction of the two mayors.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have full confidence that we will get there,\\\" LA Mayor Eric Garcetti said at a celebratory news conference for both candidates and IOC President Thomas Bach.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Garcetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eric Garcetti\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Garcetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Garcetti\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Garcetti and Anne Hidalgo, his friend and counterpart from Paris, had emerged on stage seconds after the vote, holding hands, to welcome the decision.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were joined by Bach, who raised an arm of each in a shared gesture of triumph.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.146260960335055e-14, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mood looked set to continue over dinner at the IOC's favored five-star hotel, the Lausanne Palace.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Franco-American alliance continues later this week.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. President Donald Trump is due in Paris to join President Emmanuel Macron for Bastille Day on Friday, the national holiday.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.921420175257486e-11, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron was in the Olympic capital city Tuesday to promoting the Parisian cause - in a closed-door session with IOC members to explain how they would host the 2024 Olympics, and a subsequent news conference.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.43889278892688e-30, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The presidential push was judged necessary by Paris, which has failed with three recent Olympic bids.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We lost three times, we do not want to lose a fourth one,\\\" Macron said at the news conference.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.43889278892688e-30, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am here to convey the message that there is a strong unity to back this candidacy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minutes after Macron spoke, Trump wrote on Twitter: \\\"Working hard to get the Olympics for the United States (L.A.).\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1861, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.43889278892688e-30, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999986598596, \"rank\": 1.3401325028941674e-09, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1890, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.9999999998981366, \"rank\": 1.017504899739205e-10, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9958855963798421, \"rank\": 0.004131398286596079, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay tuned!\\\"\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even without help from heads of state, LA and Paris are likely to reach a deal.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A head-to-head fight for 2024 would create a loser that is unlikely to return four years later for a new 2028 bid contest.\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both of us will find it more and more difficult to convince cities - whether it's Paris, Los Angeles or other American cities - to really go into this process if one of us gets turned down,\\\" Garcetti had said earlier Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3328272467595065e-14, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.560708891716453e-11, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A deal to make both cities winners would fulfil a strategy that Bach set in motion last December to help safeguard a stable future for the signature Olympic event.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.146260960335055e-14, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked when a 2024-2028 agreement could be sealed, Bach suggested: \\\"If you ask me, I hope that in August we could be there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.146260960335055e-14, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC approved the expected double award after hearing both cities present their 2024 hosting plans at a conference center in its home city.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2703, \"end\": 2706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both cities used 45 minutes of videos and speeches in a closed-door session with IOC members to explain how they would host the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2924, \"end\": 2927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At separate news conferences, the mayors said they could work toward a deal.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We look forward to working together, maybe not in competition but collaboration with Paris,\\\" Garcetti said.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Garcetti and Hidalgo have long touted their good relations, and on Tuesday noted their cities' common positions on issues such as climate change and welcoming refugees.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.770378960109058e-19, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hidalgo cited her friendship with Garcetti as potentially a \\\"key element\\\" in the expected deal.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The dual award can give the IOC a decade of stability with two world-class cities touting financially secure bids.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3470, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2389050102239807e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LA plans to use only existing venues with zero risk of white elephants.\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows years of overspending by Olympic hosts and a series of political defeats that have sunk the campaigns of potential candidates.\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It also avoids inflicting a third recent defeat on Paris - which lost with bids for the 2008 and 2012 Olympics - and the United States.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3821, \"end\": 3826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1808808974527697e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3891, \"end\": 3904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9958855963798421, \"rank\": 0.004131398286596079, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New York and Chicago both lost heavily for 2012 and 2016, respectively.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3906, \"end\": 3914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999998976818, \"rank\": 8.080833286984693e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 3919, \"end\": 3926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9999999856549949, \"rank\": 9.341776288832324e-09, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbp